cs.CE, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.NE

The paper discusses an online education and training platform that focuses on deep learning and accelerated computing. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Computer Engineering (cs.CE), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Of these, cs.CE and cs.LG are the most likely categories, as they directly relate to the content of the paper. However, cs.DC, cs.CV, and cs.NE are also possible categories, as they are related to the use of parallel and distributed computing, computer vision, and neural networks, respectively.
